	'custom-shipping-declarations' => array(
		'intro' => 'UAE customs declaration registry mapped from the C&L Excel format — 36 declaration types across import, export, transit, temporary admission, and transfer, plus LGP warehouse intake. Dashboard KPIs, category lists, core field capture, and Phase 2 reports (search, cost summary, duty stub, re-export, document expiry) are live in ERP.', 
